  <summary date="2021-01-11T19:50:35Z" status="Introduced in Senate">COVID-19 Vaccine Awareness Support Act of 2020

This bill requires the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention to award grants to state, tribal, territorial, and local health departments or nonprofits to disseminate information about COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019), including regarding the safety and efficacy of vaccines.</summary>
